<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Gibang Khenni</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Alang dahna lenvui a kai,
 Simlei gamdai ah;
 Lalpa mina guol lungtuok te,
 Khenna kawlni a suok.

[V2]
 Gibang khen zo puong ie (2)
 Aw ka len-guol ngaihte,
 Lalpa, Na Lautha hung lengin,
 Sun naubang ei nemin.

[V3]
 2. Sun leh zanin ninnawp zai lan,
 Na min ka pak ui;
 Gibang khenna lenkawl a eng,
 Albang dahnan ei bawm.

[V4]
 3. Na sakmin chem bang chawian kau,
 Lautha ninnawp na'n;
 Na lungsiet lenvui kai nuoiah,
 Van mi nun ka sin ui.

[V5]
 4. Gibang kikhen mah leu ungle,
 Lautha ei puiin;
 Lungkham lenpul khuombang do hi,
 Naubang ei hung nemin.</lyrics>
<author>Lianvela</author>
<hymn_number>276</hymn_number>
</song>